Blueberry Cake
2 c flour
1.5 c sugar 
2 teaspoons of baking powder
2 eggs
1 c milk
2 c blueberries
2/3 c of butter

Soften butter
Combine all items 
Put in pan
Sprinkle 1/4 of sugar on top
Cook a 350F for 40-45 min
